<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.4">
<l>vaḷarntavaṉait taṭaṅkaṭaluḷ valiyuruviṉ tiricakaṭam</l>
<l>taḷarntutira vutaittavaṉait tariyātaṉ ṟiraṇiyaṉaip</l>
<l>piḷantavaṉai perunilamī raṭinīṭṭip paṇṭorunāḷ</l>
<l>aḷantavaṉai yāṉkaṇṭa taṇinīrtteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beholding of the one who slept in the vast sea, the one who kicked</l>
<l>So the whirling, powerfully-formed cart, weakened and was demolished,</l>
<l>The one who split Hiraṇya that day, being intolerant [of him],</l>
<l>Who measured the vast land, stretching forth his two feet one day long ago,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Araṅkam of the South by lovely waters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
